text: numbala ha numbalage pravahana satun bhukti vidinu pinisa muhudu satun dandayam kirima ha eya aharayata gænima numbalata anumata karana ladi. namut ihram tattvaye sitina kaltak godabima satun dandayam kirima numbalata tahanam karana ladi. tavada numbala kavareku veta ek ræs karanu labannehu da evan allahta numbala biya bætimat vanu
